23/05/2010
BELGRADE, Serbia -- The Holy Synod of the Serbian Orthodox Church (SPC) appointed Bishop of Montenegro and the Coast Amfilohije as the new church leader in Kosovo on Friday (May 21st).
He replaces Archbishop Artemije, who was removed from the post in early May, after being suspended amid an embezzlement scandal (Tanjug, Beta, B92, RTS - 21/05/10)
